{"lemma":"أَعْشَى","slug":"أَعْشَى","root":"ع.ش.#","root_slug":"ع-ش-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ش-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29257"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"having a poor vision"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From عَشَا (ʕašā)."},"ipa":["/ʔaʕ.ʃaː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29257","headword_ar":"اَعْشَى","root":"E$w","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weak-sighted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sightless by night, but seeing by day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having bad sight by night and by day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$","text_ar":"عَش","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$owaA='u","text_ar":"عَشْوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) applied to a woman; (S, Msb;) [the masc. being applied to a man, and either masc. or fem. to a beast of the equine kind, and a camel, and a bird, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$FA","text_ar":"عَشًا"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] and dual masc."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo$ayaAni","text_ar":"اَعْشَيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$owaAwaAni","text_ar":"عَشْوَاوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) [and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$oYN","text_ar":"عُشْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  The fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$owaA='u","text_ar":"عَشْوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also particularly signifies. A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that sees not before her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has weak sight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and therefore strikes everything with her fore feet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not paying attention to the places of her feet"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [Hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiba fulaAnN AlEa$owaA='a","text_ar":"رَكِبَ فُلَانٌ العَشْوَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one prosecuted his affair without mental perception,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without certainty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabaTahu xaboTa","text_ar":"خَبَطَهُ خَبْطَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$owaA='a","text_ar":"عَشْوَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at random,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without aim;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus accord. to the M: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be ventured upon it without mental perception,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without certainty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it upon himself without his endeavouring to ascertain the right course;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the doing of which is sometimes, or often, attended with error: it is a prov., applied to him who goes at random and does not care for the result of his conduct. (TA. [See also 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xbT","text_ar":"خبط"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqaAbN Ea$owaA='u","text_ar":"عُقَابٌ عَشْوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eagle that cares not how it beats the ground, and where it strikes with its talons."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  See also the fem. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$owapN","text_ar":"عَشْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}